metadata.description:
In a smokeless city, there was a woman shining under neon lights. Her name was Aya. With her stunning beauty and bionic implants, Aya represented the free spirit of the cyberpunk world.

Aya had fled the corrupt system of an old corporation and joined the underground resistance. This resistance was home to a group of rebellious spirits who fought against the corporations' tyrannical rule. Aya was a warrior fighting for freedom and justice.
